    {
        "content": "<p><span aria-label=\"speech balloon\" class=\"emoji emoji-1f4ac\" role=\"img\" title=\"speech balloon\">:speech_balloon:</span> bjorn3 created <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/13815#discussion_r3522853228\">PR review comment</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>cg_clif would at the very least need the thumb2 (use thumb2 rather than the original thumb) and thumb-mode (actually use thumb rather than arm instructions) settings to match LLVM. And the current backend you wrote should error when either is not set.</p>\n</blockquote>",
