    {
        "content": "<p><span aria-label=\"speech balloon\" class=\"emoji emoji-1f4ac\" role=\"img\" title=\"speech balloon\">:speech_balloon:</span> cpetig created <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/13815#discussion_r3525803476\">PR review comment</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>I think you mean these subtarget flags: <a href=\"https://github.com/llvm/llvm-project/blob/main/llvm/lib/Target/ARM/ARMSubtarget.h\">https://github.com/llvm/llvm-project/blob/main/llvm/lib/Target/ARM/ARMSubtarget.h</a> and <a href=\"https://github.com/llvm/llvm-project/blob/main/llvm/include/llvm/TargetParser/Triple.h\">https://github.com/llvm/llvm-project/blob/main/llvm/include/llvm/TargetParser/Triple.h</a> - but at least thumb vs arm is selected by the target triple.</p>\n</blockquote>",
