        "content": "<p>fitzgen <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/13815#issuecomment-4896250333\">commented</a> on <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/13815\">PR #13815</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Moving review to @cfallin because (a) I'm not really knowledgeable about arm32 and (b) I will be out of office next week and don't have time to look at it this week.</p>\n</blockquote>",
