    {
        "content": "<p>cfallin <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/13815#issuecomment-4896282836\">commented</a> on <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/13815\">PR #13815</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>(I'm also on PTO this week, and traveling next week, so I will look at this the week of Mon Jul 20; happy to do so of course)</p>\n</blockquote>",
